     H            Y.
     F** AM#R22E ********************************************
     F* RETURN #OF MANIFESTS with Exception Code
     F*    LEC.             2019.03.13                      *
     F*******************************************************
     FAM#PL22 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     E                    MAN       300 50
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60STIME
      *
      * 2D MANIFEST BARCODE
     I            DS
     I                                        1  50 MFBC
     I                                        1   5 MFNAMC
     I                                        6  10 MFSUPP
     I                                       11  12 MFDOCK
     I                                       13  24 MFORD#
     I                                       25  33 MFMRTE
     I                                       34  36 MFSDCK
     I                                       37  38 MFPALT
     I                                       39  40 MFMROS
     I                                       41  44 MFSKID
     I                                       44  44 MFSIDE
     I                                       45  50 MFFILR
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           SURT    7
     C                     PARM           SHID    8
     C                     PARM           SHIT    6
     C                     PARM           EXCD    3
     C                     PARM           P2EXTL  30
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * MAIN                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           KEY01     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KKSURT  9
     C                     KFLD           KKSHID  8
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     MOVELSURT      KKSURT  9
     C                     MOVELSHID      KKSHID  8
      *
      * for truck (route) and ship date and exception code,
      * get number of manifests scanned.
     C                     Z-ADD0         P2EXTL
      *
     C           KEY01     SETLLAM#PL22
     C           KEY01     READEAM#PL22                  50
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ'0'
      *
     C           R2SKJY    IFEQ ' '
     C           R2HNTE    ANDEQ'OK'
     C           R2EXCD    ANDEQEXCD
     C           R2SHIT    ANDEQSHIT
     C                     ADD  1         P2EXTL
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KEY01     READEAM#PL22                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
